- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is relevant as the paper deals with forensic investigations of terrorist attacks.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with indexing and searching large amounts of video footage.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper mentions the use of analytical modules and similarity search, which are often based on machine learning techniques.
